Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:19.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Where is the truths
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:34.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今無情一帯の世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Here is no truths
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}栄光もなく奪い合う
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It's like a party
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}交錯する者たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}突き進め果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:47.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}勝者と敗者どちらも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:48.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}maybe something crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:50.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}What can I belive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:53.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そんな問いなんで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:55.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}No one answer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:09:01.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}すべてこの虚空の中消えてった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:06.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今はBREAK OUT BREAK OUT進めよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:07.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:12.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}その意志を揚げて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:15.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあもっとBREAK OUT BREAK OUT世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:22.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}切り開け迷っても
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:25.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}So we gatta just go crazy,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:26.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}just go crazy now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:29.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}dance,dance crazy ,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:32.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢か地獄かGO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:19.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理何處尋覓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:34.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}眼前這冷酷無情的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理無從尋覓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}僅有骯髒的搶與奪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就像一場派對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}命運縱橫交錯的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向著終點一意前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:47.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}無論勝者或敗者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:48.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}或許某物已然瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:50.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何物可信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:53.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如此疑問為何…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:55.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}無人作答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:09:01.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一切盡皆消失在這片虛無之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:06.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}現在BREAK OUT BREAK OUT  前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:07.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:12.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}高舉這份決心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:15.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}來吧  繼續BREAK OUT BREAK OUT突破
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:22.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界的束縛  即使迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:25.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我們只需變得瘋狂  瘋而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:26.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如今只需變得瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:29.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}舞蹈  舞至瘋狂  瘋而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:32.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢或地獄  GO CRY GO
